## Features
- This repository contains the reusable GitHub workflow templates for.
. Validate CloudFormation templates
. Create Pipeline
. Checkov Scan
. Create Pull Request
. Drift Detection
. Infracost
. Release
. Setup Repository
. Upload CloudFormation templates to S3 bucket
. Destroy the stack